<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Goa Package</title>
    <style>
        body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #333;
}

header {
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}

nav {
    background: #f4f4f4;
    padding: 1rem;
    text-align: center;
}

nav a {
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.main {
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: right;
}
.package-details {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8ccfa;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

.package-details h1 {
    text-align: center;
    color: #2c3e50;
}

.package-details h2 {
    color: #e74c3c;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

.package-details ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.package-details ul ul {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 20px;
}

.package-details ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

footer {
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 100%;
}

        /

        .contact-form {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 400px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .contact-form h1 {
           
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: larger;
        }
        .contact-form select {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: larger;
        }

        .contact-form button {
            width: 20%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .contact-form button:hover {
            background-color: #555;
        }

        .contact-form .success-message {
            display: none;
            color: green;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        {{> header }}
    </header>
    
    {{> navbar }}
    
    <main>
        <section class="package-details">
            <h1>Goa Package</h1>
            <h2>Price:</h2>
            <p><em>₹25,000 per person</em></p>
            <h2>Duration:</h2>
            <p><em>5 Days / 4 Nights</em></p>

            <h2>Package Inclusions:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h3>Accommodation:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>4 nights stay in a 4-star beach resort with sea view rooms.</li>
                        <li>Complimentary breakfast included.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Travel:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Round-trip airfare from major cities.</li>
                        <li>Airport transfers in a comfortable air-conditioned vehicle.</li>
                        <li>Daily transportation for sightseeing in a private car.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Sightseeing and Activities:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Day 1: Arrival and Relaxation</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Welcome drink on arrival.</li>
                                <li>Check-in and relax at the beach resort.</li>
                                <li>Evening at leisure to explore the local beach.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Day 2: North Goa Tour</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Visit Calangute, Baga, and Anjuna beaches.</li>
                                <li>Explore Fort Aguada and its lighthouse.</li>
                                <li>Experience the vibrant nightlife at Tito's Street.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Day 3: South Goa Tour</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Visit Colva, Palolem, and Benaulim beaches.</li>
                                <li>Explore the historic Basilica of Bom Jesus and Se Cathedral.</li>
                                <li>Enjoy a serene boat cruise on the Mandovi River.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Day 4: Adventure and Water Sports</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Engage in exciting water sports activities like parasailing, jet-skiing, and banana boat rides.</li>
                                <li>Visit Dudhsagar Waterfalls and take a jeep safari.</li>
                                <li>Relax at the resort in the evening with a special Goan dinner.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Day 5: Departure</strong>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Breakfast at the resort.</li>
                                <li>Check-out and transfer to the airport for your flight back home.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Meals:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Daily breakfast at the hotel.</li>
                        <li>Special Goan dinner on Day 4.</li>
                        <li>Optional lunch and dinner at recommended local restaurants (additional cost).</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h3>Additional Benefits:</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Free Wi-Fi at the hotel.</li>
                        <li>Access to the hotel’s swimming pool and gym.</li>
                        <li>Travel insurance coverage.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Terms and Conditions:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Prices are per person based on double occupancy.</li>
                <li>Flights are subject to availability.</li>
                <li>Itinerary may change based on weather and other conditions.</li>
                <li>Travel insurance is mandatory for all travelers.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Booking Information:</h2>
            <p>For more details and booking, please visit our website or contact our customer service.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    

    <div class="contact-form">
        <h1>Book Rooms</h1>
        <form id="contact-form" action="">
            <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
            <select name="hotel" id="contact-form">
                <option value="single">Single Room</option>
                <option value="double">Double Room</option>
                <option value="double\Ac">Double Room\AC</option>
            </select>
            <select name="price" id="contact-form">
                <option value="single">4000</option>
                <option value="double">9000</option>
                <option value="double\Ac">12000</option>
            </select>
            <button class="btn" onclick= "window.location.href = 'https://wa.me/+917904946778';">Click Here</button>
        </form>
        <div class="success-message" id="success-message">
            Thank you! Your message has been sent.
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('contact-form').addEventListener('submit', function (event) {
            event.preventDefault();
            // Simulate form submission success
            document.getElementById('success-message').style.display = 'block';
            document.getElementById('contact-form').reset();
        });
    </script>
    <br><br><br><br><br>



    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Travel Trip Service Provider. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    
</body>

</html>
